quran[7]{c,v,t}:
  29,46,aur ehley kitaab se jhagra nah karo magar aisay tareeq se ke nihayat acha ho. haan jo unn mein se be insafi karen ( unn ke sath isi terhan majadla karo ) aur keh do ke jo ( kitaab ) hum par utreen aur jo ( kitaaben ) tum par Utrain hum sab par imaan rakhtay hain aur hamara aur tumhara mabood aik hi hai aur hum usi ke farmanbardar hain
  29,47,aur isi terhan hum ne tumhari taraf kitaab aُtari hai. to jin logon ko hum ne kitaaben di theen woh is par imaan le atay hain. aur baaz un ( mushriq ) logon mein se bhi is par imaan le atay hain. aur hamari aayton se wohi inkaar karte hain jo kafir ( Azli ) hain
  29,48,aur tum is se pehlay koi kitaab nahi parhte they aur nah ussay apne haath se likh hi satke they aisa hota to ehley baatil zaroor shak karte
  29,49,balkay yeh roshan ayatain hain. jin logon ko ilm diya gaya hai unn ke seenon mein ( mehfooz ) aur hamari aayton se wohi log inkaar karte hain jo be insaaf hain
  29,50,aur ( kafir ) kehte hain ke is par is ke perwar-digaar ki taraf se nishanain kyun nazil nahi huien keh do ke nishanain to khuda hi ke paas hain. aur mein to khullam khula hadaayat karne wala hon
  29,51,kiya unn logon ke liye yeh kaafi nahi ke hum ne tum par kitaab nazil ki jo unn ko parh kar sunai jati hai. kuch shak nahi ke momin logon ke liye is mein rehmat aur nasiyaat hai
  29,52,keh do ke mere aur tumahray darmain khuda hi gawah kaafi hai jo cheez asmano mein aur zameen mein hai woh sab ko jaanta hai. aur jin logon ne baatil ko maana aur khuda se inkaarkiya wohi nuqsaan aُthane walay hain
